    <!-- How to Get Started Section (updated with red theme) -->
<section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-4">
            How to <span class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400">Get Started</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Joining Eternity Care Services' Day Program is a simple and supportive process designed to ensure you get the most out of your experience. From the initial consultation to tailored assessments and ongoing support, we guide you through every step. Our team will help you understand your NDIS funding, personalise your program based on your needs, and ensure a smooth transition into engaging activities that promote independence, social connections, and personal growth.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Steps Grid with Remixicon Icons -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        
        <!-- Step 1: Contact Us -->
        <div class="step-card bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
            <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="step-icon mr-3 text-2xl w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="ri-phone-line text-red-600 dark:text-red-400"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-2">Contact Us</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">
                        Reach out to our friendly team at Eternity Care Services to discuss your needs, goals, and expectations from the program. Whether you're looking for social engagement, skill development, or structured daytime support, we'll guide you through the available options and help you understand how our program can best support you.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2: Check Your NDIS Funding -->
        <div class="step-card bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
            <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="step-icon mr-3 text-2xl w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="ri-funds-line text-red-600 dark:text-red-400"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-2">Check Your NDIS Funding</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">
                        Before enrolling in the program, it's important to ensure you have the appropriate NDIS funding available under your plan. Our team can help you understand your funding eligibility and guide you on how to allocate the necessary budget for day program participation. If you're unsure, we can also assist you in navigating NDIS plan reviews or modifications.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3: Personalised Assessment -->
        <div class="step-card bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
            <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="step-icon mr-3 text-2xl w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="ri-file-list-line text-red-600 dark:text-red-400"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-2">Personalised Assessment</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">
                        Once your funding is confirmed, we'll conduct a detailed assessment to better understand your specific requirements, interests, and preferences. This helps us tailor the program to ensure you get the most out of your experience, whether it's social activities, skill-building sessions, or therapeutic engagements.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4: Join the Program -->
        <div class="step-card bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
            <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="step-icon mr-3 text-2xl w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="ri-calendar-check-line text-red-600 dark:text-red-400"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-2">Join the Program</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">
                        After the assessment, we'll finalise the details and set up a schedule that works best for you. Whether you choose to attend a few days a week or regularly participate, we ensure a smooth transition into the program so you feel comfortable and supported from day one.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 5: Ongoing Support & Progress Monitoring -->
        <div class="step-card bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
            <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="step-icon mr-3 text-2xl w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <i class="ri-heart-pulse-line text-red-600 dark:text-red-400"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-2">Ongoing Support & Progress Monitoring</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">
                        At Eternity Care Services, we are committed to your continuous growth and well-being. Our team will regularly check in with you to assess your experience, gather feedback, and make any necessary adjustments to your activities. We work alongside you and your support network to ensure you're getting the most value from our day program.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Extra Note -->
        <div class="step-card bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md col-span-1 md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-3">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
